WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:21.053 --> 00:00:23.858
We used to come up here
when we were kids.

00:00:24.322 --> 00:00:27.662
Even before we could drive
we'd cut class, sneak out,

00:00:27.726 --> 00:00:30.298
come up here, and watch
the older kids drift.

00:00:37.003 --> 00:00:39.041
Things were different
back then.

00:00:43.077 --> 00:00:45.916
Once l got my license,
l practically lived up here.

00:00:46.514 --> 00:00:49.086
Back then, kids iust drove
whatever they had.

00:00:49.250 --> 00:00:50.518
You know, we just made do.

00:00:50.651 --> 00:00:51.920
No one bothered us.

00:00:53.354 --> 00:00:54.890
The day l got my license

00:00:54.956 --> 00:00:57.461
is the day l got
my first speeding ticket.

00:00:57.526 --> 00:00:59.931
The day after that,
l won my first race.

00:01:00.429 --> 00:01:03.001
l beat this rich kid
by three lengths.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.739
l gotta admit, it felt good.

00:01:08.538 --> 00:01:09.841
lt felt like...

00:01:10.107 --> 00:01:12.344
Like everything else
just disappears.

00:01:14.345 --> 00:01:15.847
No past and no future.

00:01:16.380 --> 00:01:17.916
No problems.

00:01:19.884 --> 00:01:21.486
Just the moment.

